{"type":"message","id":"4f0e2364","parentId":"f6b55d51","timestamp":"2026-04-09T00:46:39.038Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Based on the memory search results, I can see the context about \"系统门控关闭\" (system gate closure). The key information is from session f2acef4e-bf1f-42b5-91dd-dc1eca60ab32.jsonl.\n\nThe system gate was closed (FULL_HALT triggered) because:\n1. Market data was stuck at March 31st (清明节/Tomb Sweeping Day holiday caused data gap)\n2. Dashboard data was stale (paper portfolio comparison last updated March 31, paper holdings data from April 3)\n3. The strict gate was triggered due to `dashboard_fresh = False`\n\nThis was from around April 7-9, 2026. The user is asking about this today (April 9, 2026).\n\nLet me provide a clear answer based on what I found in memory.","thinkingSignature":"89d4344dd0c017debc8e198f9b68c4a2e0466b436d500ce03b2aa1bbfa174af7"},{"type":"text","text":"根据之前的记录，系统门控（strict gate）关闭的根因是：\n\n**行情数据卡在 3月31日**，清明节假期导致日线数据断档，触发链是：\n\n```\n行情数据3月31日 → 清明假期后无更新 → generate_live_candidates 失败\n→ 纸盘对比仪表盘无法刷新 → dashboard_fresh = False\n→ strict_gate = True → runtime_ready = False → FULL_HALT\n```\n\n仪表盘数据最后更新是 **3月31日**，落后了 7 天，所以严格门控被触发，系统判定当前不能输出可执行买价，买入被阻断。\n\n今天是 4月9日，收盘后数据应该已经更新。你现在是想让我检查一下系统门控是否已经恢复正常吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4201,"output":342,"cacheRead":19969,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24512,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775695587958,"responseId":"062629e40f2980fa25d504a5150d6c52"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cffe6660","parentId":"4f0e2364","timestamp":"2026-04-09T00:51:12.418Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b525b310440b4c148de12e397d59\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-09 08:51 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b525b310440b4c148de12e397d59]\n张玲: 你应该自动更新数据啊"}],"timestamp":1775695872416}}
{"type":"message","id":"08f70847","parentId":"cffe6660","timestamp":"2026-04-09T00:51:22.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"你应该自动更新数据啊\" - meaning \"You should automatically update the data!\" They seem frustrated that the system didn't automatically recover after the Qingming holiday.\n\nLet me check the current state of the system - are the cron jobs running? Did the data actually update after the market closed yesterday (April 8)? I should check the current status of the data and the cron setup.\n\nIt's currently April 9, 08:51 AM - before market open (09:30). The data from yesterday (April 8) should have been updated after the market closed at 15:00. But wait - did the cron job actually run?\n\n\nI need to verify whether yesterday's data actually made it into the system.","thinkingSignature":"b9f7ff8065703403739b0f9348fe6ca45bd1fdfdab19881c666f1a8ef7eb0972"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，这是清明后数据断了但自动化没跟上。我来看看现在数据恢复情况和 cron 定时任务的设置。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gkm6sa0ivsvo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent/paper_trade/dashboard/market_profile/ 2>/dev/null | tail -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gkm6sa0ivsvo_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent/paper_trade/output/current_paper*/ 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"最新|latest\" | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77,"output":282,"cacheRead":19969,"cacheWrite":4424,"totalTokens":24752,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775695872421,"responseId":"06262b004116d3ab61e478a15c25cbc0"}}
