{"type":"message","id":"2c7394fd","parentId":"b656112f","timestamp":"2026-04-09T00:52:24.665Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e0vdocp8bo63_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"-rw-------  1 ling  staff  - 8977 Apr  7 10:30 /Volumes/A/openclaw-cold/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/industries.csv"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":15,"aggregated":"-rw-------  1 ling  staff  - 8977 Apr  7 10:30 /Volumes/A/openclaw-cold/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/industries.csv","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775695944660}}
{"type":"message","id":"23a8e5e3","parentId":"2c7394fd","timestamp":"2026-04-09T00:52:24.669Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e0vdocp8bo63_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n行业板块数据同步脚本 — 基于新浪财经行业板块接口\n每天交易时段自动运行，将数据写入 data/industries.csv\n\n数据源: https://vip.stock.finance.sina.com.cn/q/view/newFLJK.php?param=class\n接口说明: 新浪财经行业板块，含板块名称、涨跌幅、上涨/下跌家数、领涨股\n\n⚠️ 清明假期（4/4-4/6）休市，数据为假期后首个交易日实时数据\n\"\"\"\nimport csv\nimport json\nimport re\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime, date\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# .../personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/sync_sector_board_data.py\n# parent = scripts/, grandparent = project root\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parent.parent\nOUTPUT_CSV = PROJECT_ROOT / \"data\" / \"industries.csv\"\nOUTPUT_JSON = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\" / \"sector_heatmap_summary.json\"\nREPORTS_DIR = OUTPUT_JSON.parent\n\n\ndef fetch_sina_sector_board() -> list[dict]:\n    \"\"\"\n    从新浪财经获取行业板块数据\n    返回: [{code, name, num_stocks, change_pct, up_count, down_count, leader, leader_pct}, ...]\n    \"\"\"\n    url = \"https://vip.stock.finance.sina.com.cn/q/view/newFLJK.php?param=class\"\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers={\n        \"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0\",\n        \"Referer\": \"https://finance.sina.com.cn/\"\n    })\n    resp = urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=10)\n    raw = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\", errors=\"replace\")\n\n    # 解析 var S_Finance_bankuai_class = {...}\n    header_match = re.match(r\"var S_Finance_bankuai_class = (.+)\", raw.strip())"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":15,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n行业板块数据同步脚本 — 基于新浪财经行业板块接口\n每天交易时段自动运行，将数据写入 data/industries.csv\n\n数据源: https://vip.stock.finance.sina.com.cn/q/view/newFLJK.php?param=class\n接口说明: 新浪财经行业板块，含板块名称、涨跌幅、上涨/下跌家数、领涨股\n\n⚠️ 清明假期（4/4-4/6）休市，数据为假期后首个交易日实时数据\n\"\"\"\nimport csv\nimport json\nimport re\nimport urllib.request\nfrom datetime import datetime, date\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# .../personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/sync_sector_board_data.py\n# parent = scripts/, grandparent = project root\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parent.parent\nOUTPUT_CSV = PROJECT_ROOT / \"data\" / \"industries.csv\"\nOUTPUT_JSON = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\" / \"sector_heatmap_summary.json\"\nREPORTS_DIR = OUTPUT_JSON.parent\n\n\ndef fetch_sina_sector_board() -> list[dict]:\n    \"\"\"\n    从新浪财经获取行业板块数据\n    返回: [{code, name, num_stocks, change_pct, up_count, down_count, leader, leader_pct}, ...]\n    \"\"\"\n    url = \"https://vip.stock.finance.sina.com.cn/q/view/newFLJK.php?param=class\"\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers={\n        \"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0\",\n        \"Referer\": \"https://finance.sina.com.cn/\"\n    })\n    resp = urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=10)\n    raw = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\", errors=\"replace\")\n\n    # 解析 var S_Finance_bankuai_class = {...}\n    header_match = re.match(r\"var S_Finance_bankuai_class = (.+)\", raw.strip())","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775695944665}}
{"type":"message","id":"abe69844","parentId":"23a8e5e3","timestamp":"2026-04-09T00:52:33.852Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file is owned by `ling` with no special flags. The write fails with `Operation not permitted`. This is very strange.\n\nWait - let me think about this differently. The `cron` is running as root (as shown by `ps aux`). But the crontab is configured for the user `ling`. In macOS, when a user sets up a crontab, the jobs run as that user. So it should run as `ling`, not root.\n\nBut the `Operation not permitted` error on a file you own... Let me think about this more.\n\nActually - could this be a **System Integrity Protection (SIP)** issue with `/Volumes/A/` being on an external drive? Or could there be an **Apple Double Store** (._ files) or an extended attribute issue?\n\n\nLet me try writing directly to that file to see what error I actually get.","thinkingSignature":"94c845e4ab2b78968262a565e026248f8be39fe605deefc8c86464b925665f69"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oyhv8an3xchw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test write directly\npython3 -c \"\nwith open('/Volumes/A/openclaw-cold/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/industries.csv', 'a') as f:\n    f.write('test')\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9833,"output":257,"cacheRead":19969,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30059,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775695944669,"responseId":"06262b491d0f65203717e0be2a09a194"}}
