{"type":"message","id":"6f46fc44","parentId":"edb0cf07","timestamp":"2026-04-09T00:57:33.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The launchd agent is loaded (status 0 means it's been loaded, even if `0` PID means it's not currently running - it's a scheduled job, not a persistent daemon).Wait - `launchctl list` shows:\n```\n-\t0\tai.openclaw.quant.sector-sync\n```\n`- 0` means the process is not running but has been loaded. This is expected for a scheduled (calendar) launchd agent. It will run at the scheduled times.\n\nThe manual run succeeded. Both CSV and JSON are saved. Now let me also fix the `precheck` and `strategy_report` cron jobs to use launchd agents too.","thinkingSignature":"7ea8d4e99c9e5fca55b8178ff17b89681ffb20a4a00e0d5cd65fd6529e067b0a"},{"type":"text","text":"Launchd agent 已加载，脚本正常运行。`96.6% 板块上涨`，今天市场非常强势。\n\n现在把其他 cron job 也迁移到 launchd，确保盘前 09:20 的强检和策略报告也自动跑：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lpgh0fc9jrdg_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.openclaw.quant.precheck.plist","content":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC \"-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN\" \"http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd\">\n<plist version=\"1.0\">\n<dict>\n    <key>Label</key>\n    <string>ai.openclaw.quant.precheck</string>\n    <key>User</key>\n    <string>ling</string>\n    <key>ProgramArguments</key>\n    <array>\n        <string>/usr/bin/python3</string>\n        <string>/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py</string>\n        <string>--available-cash</string>\n        <string>1000000</string>\n        <string>--account-nav</string>\n        <string>930000</string>\n    </array>\n    <key>WorkingDirectory</key>\n    <string>/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system</string>\n    <key>StandardOutPath</key>\n    <string>/Users/ling/.open