{"type":"message","id":"28a5ef69","parentId":"e2f23278","timestamp":"2026-04-09T01:12:17.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me summarize what local models are available and what they can do.\n\nCurrent setup:\n- Ollama running locally at localhost:11434\n- 4 models: my-qwen (Qwen3.5-9B), gemma3:4b, deepseek-r1:7b, carstenuhlig/omnicoder-9b:latest\n- oMLX running at localhost:8000 with Qwen2.5-0.5B and Qwen2.5-1.5B\n\nBut the current session is using MiniMax-M2.7 from the minimax portal, not the local models. The model aliases are empty, meaning no local shortcuts are configured.","thinkingSignature":"5eed6c88a51a1ff54215a8fddee56d84103e718bfe6fc5d8ea899c0786b64eed"},{"type":"text","text":"你有 4 个本地模型在跑，总结如下：\n\n**Ollama（localhost:11434）**\n| 模型 | 大小 | 用途 | 特点 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| `my-qwen` (Qwen3.5-9B) | 5.7GB | 主力本地模型 | 32K 上下文，**支持推理（thinking）**，工具调用不支持 |\n| `deepseek-r1:7b` | 4.7GB | 深度推理 | 32K 上下文，**支持推理**，适合复杂分析 |\n| `gemma3:4b` | 1.2GB | 轻量快速 | 4K 上下文，不支持推理，**最快最省显存** |\n| `omnicoder-9b` | 5.7GB | 代码专用 | 32K 上下文，代码生成优化 |\n\n**oMLX（localhost:8000）**\n| 模型 | 大小 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Qwen2.5-0.5B | ~1GB | 极轻量场景 |\n| Qwen2.5-1.5B | ~2GB | 轻量对话 |\n\n---\n\n**能干什么？**\n\n1. **纯本地对话/写作**（完全离线，不走 API）\n2. **深度推理分析**：`deepseek-r1` 适合复杂逻辑问题\n3. **代码生成**：`omnicoder-9b` 专攻代码，`my-qwen` 通用也行\n4. **量化策略分析**：本地跑数据处理、指标计算、策略回测逻辑\n5. **作为 MiniMax 的备用**：当网络/API 受限时本地接管\n\n**目前限制：**\n- 没有配置模型别名（如 `qwen-local` → `my-qwen`），需要手动指定模型\n- 工具调用（function calling）不支持，本地模型只能做文字生成\n- 现在的 session 用的是 MiniMax-M2.7，不是本地模型\n\n你想用本地模型跑什么具体任务吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22961,"output":590,"cacheRead":19969,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43520,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775697119096,"responseId":"06262fdf17379ebac5ab5be292b71bed"}}
