{"type":"message","id":"5e5f32f5","parentId":"b2c2e836","timestamp":"2026-04-09T01:15:46.861Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see an issue - the ollama list shows `my-qwen:latest` not `my-qwen`, and `bge-m3:latest` not `gemma3:4b`. The model IDs in openclaw.json need to match the actual model names from ollama. Let me fix this.\n\nAlso, `gemma3:4b` isn't installed, and `my-qwen` should be `my-qwen:latest`.\n\nLet me update the aliases to use the correct model IDs.","thinkingSignature":"58161ae136669f5596dfb13f8546e97de207f73ef55cfcd1c20b592adde26984"},{"type":"text","text":"`my-qwen` 和 `gemma3:4b` 的 ID 不对，Ollama 里实际叫 `my-qwen:latest` 和没有装 `gemma3`。来修正：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gb81f6otf5mx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Fix the aliases with correct Ollama model IDs\ncat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nd['modelAliases'] = {\n  # Ollama 本地模型（用完整的正确ID）\n  'qwen-local':      'ollama-local/my-qwen:latest',\n  'deepseek-local':  'ollama-local/deepseek-r1:7b',\n  'omnicoder-local': 'ollama-local/carstenuhlig/omnicoder-9b:latest',\n  # oMLX 轻量模型\n  'omlx-qwen-small': 'omlx/Qwen2.5-0.5B-Instruct-4bit',\n  'omlx-qwen-1.5b':   'omlx/Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct-4bit',\n}\nprint(json.dumps(d, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\n\" > /tmp/openclaw_fixed.json && mv /tmp/openclaw_fixed.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json && echo \"OK\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25081,"output":397,"cacheRead":19969,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45447,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775697337306,"responseId":"062630b9c8a38849197e139f9e3dd34b"}}
