{"type":"message","id":"de99f997","parentId":"78b7a3ed","timestamp":"2026-04-09T01:23:44.133Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We have `llama-server` (14.9MB) with Metal support (it was compiled with Metal dylibs). Now I need to:\n\n1. Install `llama-server` somewhere in PATH (like `/usr/local/bin/`)\n2. Start `llama-server` on port 8000\n3. Download GGUF models for:\n   - Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct (Q4_K_M or similar quantization)\n   - DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Qwen-7B-Q4_K_M\n   - OmniCoder (GGUF version)\n   - bge-m3 embeddings\n\nThe models will be stored in `~/.cache/huggingface/hub/` which maps to `/System/Volumes/Data/Users/ling/.cache/huggingface/`.\n\n\nI should check the disk space on that volume first.","thinkingSignature":"22de8fc06c73394893f5f926fa2b84aae2764ce4f42cc4433edd62300bf4007e"},{"type":"text","text":"`llama-server` 拿到了（含 Metal GPU 加速）。现在安装到 PATH，然后下载 GGUF 模型：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wbnhhw7cvjqe_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Install llama-server to /usr/local/bin/\ncp /tmp/llama-b8713/llama-server /usr/local/bin/llama-server && chmod +x /usr/local/bin/llama-server && echo \"✅ Installed\"\n\n# Check Metal GPU availability\n/usr/local/bin/llama-server --help 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39728,"output":296,"cacheRead":19943,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59967,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775697813452,"responseId":"06263295d4e9afe4813c697be11442f6"}}
