{"type":"message","id":"1cbff47b","parentId":"0027fc25","timestamp":"2026-04-09T01:24:16.057Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"80GB free on the data volume. That's enough for several models.Let me now:1. Start `llama-server` on port 8000 in the background2. Download the GGUF models\n\nFirst, let me start the llama-server. I'll start it in the background. The server will be the OpenAI-compatible API.Let me start it and then download the models. I'll use `huggingface-cli` or direct URLs to download the GGUF files.For the models:\n- Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct: `Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct-GGUF` (look for Q4_K_M or similar)\n\n\n- DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Qwen-7B: `DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Qwen-7B-GGUF` \n- OmniCoder: `scb10x/llama3.1-omnicoder-7b-gguf` or similar\n- bge-m3: `Xenova/bge-m3-GGUF`\n\nNow I'll get the llama-server running in the background.","thinkingSignature":"2182079928bd1ae9e9ff65e4fd2d6aaeeeb4c1aebc939534b874ebd3ac496ce7"},{"type":"text","text":"80GB 可用，足够。先在后台启动 `llama-server`，再下载模型：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s72c2iea3t2e_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Start llama-server on port 8000 with Metal GPU in background\n# Models will be loaded on-demand via /v1/models API\nnohup ~/bin/llama-server \\\n  -ngl 99 \\\n  --host 127.0.0.1 \\\n  --port 8000 \\\n  > ~/workspace/logs/llama-server.log 2>&1 &\n\necho \"PID: $!\"\nsleep 3\n\n# Verify it's running\ncurl -s http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/models 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint('✅ llama-server running!')\nprint('Available models:', [m['id'] for m in d.get('data', [])])\n\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"Server not responding yet, check logs\"\ntail -5 ~/workspace/logs/llama-server.log 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":40568,"output":474,"cacheRead":19943,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60985,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775697838727,"responseId":"062632aeceef743231dac2207b749b96"}}
