{"type":"message","id":"183e0775","parentId":"71a90df1","timestamp":"2026-04-09T01:25:28.048Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now I need to download the GGUF models. Let me search for the best variants on HuggingFace.\n\nFor the original Ollama models:\n- `my-qwen:latest` - Qwen model, likely Qwen2.5-7B or Qwen3-8B. I'll download Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct-Q4_K_M\n- `deepseek-r1:7b` - DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Qwen-7B-Q4_K_M\n- `carstenuhlig/omnicoder-9b` - This is a code model. There's no direct GGUF equivalent, but `mlx-community/Qwen2.5-7B-OmniCoder-Q4` might work. Actually looking at HuggingFace, there's `scb10x/llama3.1-omnicoder-7b-gguf` but that's Llama-based, not Qwen. \n\nFor OmniCoder specifically, I should try the HuggingFace GGUF collection even though the model ID differs from the Ollama version. For embeddings, I'll skip bge-m3 since it's less critical right now and focus on getting the core models working.\n\nNow I'm setting up a download script to pull the GGUF files directly from HuggingFace using their CLI, which will cache them in `~/.cache/huggingface/`. I'll prioritize downloading Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct-Q4_K_M and DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Qwen-7B-Q4_K_M first, then handle the embedding model separately if needed. I should create a launchd plist to keep the llama-server running persistently instead of starting it manually each time.","thinkingSignature":"75e6a201eff222d72ace0343fa92b84e28dffa64cd4c58ee76b65ac5e75fd2fe"},{"type":"text","text":"现在下载 GGUF 模型。找几个最接近原来 Ollama 模型的版本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d8hxqu63ethb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check if huggingface_hub is available\npython3 -c \"from huggingface_hub import hf_hub_download; print('✅ huggingface_hub available')\" 2>/dev/null || pip3 install huggingface-hub --quiet 2>/dev/null && python3 -c \"from huggingface_hub import hf_hub_download; print('✅ installed')\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42660,"output":473,"cacheRead":19943,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63076,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775697910980,"responseId":"062632f7c3cfe6e4e73e6ad1d6ce23b1"}}
