{"type":"message","id":"e6c2e6cc","parentId":"bfea8c82","timestamp":"2026-04-09T01:25:38.454Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me now search for the correct GGUF files for each model. I'll use the HuggingFace API to find the right files.\n\nActually, a simpler approach would be to just use `curl` to download directly from HuggingFace since the files are publicly accessible. But I need to know the exact file names first.\n\nLet me check what GGUF files are available for Qwen2.5-7B and DeepSeek-R1.\n\nActually, the easiest approach is to use `huggingface-cli` or the `huggingface_hub` Python package to list/download files. But this might take time.\n\nLet me write a script that:1. \n\nSetting up download targets...","thinkingSignature":"eebdcf3c73f07780184dca21bb4c0a97c1e1a42a91cb4d4f2027a0abc2834181"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5c8tdxcbqxur_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nfrom huggingface_hub import hf_hub_list_files\nimport json\n\n# Find Qwen2.5-7B GGUF files\nprint(\"=== Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct GGUF files ===\")\nfiles = hf_hub_list_files(\"Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct-GGUF\", gguf=True)\nfor f in files:\n    if f.endswith('.gguf'):\n        print(f)\n\nprint()\nprint(\"=== DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Qwen GGUF files ===\")\nfiles2 = hf_hub_list_files(\"deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Qwen-7B-GGUF\", gguf=True)\nfor f in files2:\n    if f.endswith('.gguf'):\n        print(f)\nEOF","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43158,"output":345,"cacheRead":19943,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63446,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775697928399,"responseId":"062633087bb8e103654c376e58511145"}}
