{"type":"message","id":"a1b5c180","parentId":"6b9faa9c","timestamp":"2026-04-09T10:14:37.032Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is installing OmniCoder and it's asking how to serve the model. They're being prompted to choose between different deployment options. Let me think about what makes sense here.\n\nThey already have:\n- llama-server running on port 8000 (we set this up earlier)\n- Ollama (but we deleted the models)\n- No vLLM, no LM Studio\n\nThe options:\n1. Tesslate cloud - free during beta, but we don't know if they have API keys\n2. Local vLLM - not installed\n3. Local llama.cpp - they have llama-server on localhost:8000 (but no models loaded yet)\n\n\n4. Local Ollama - models were deleted\n5. Local LM Studio - not installed\n6. Custom endpoint\n\nActually, I realize the OmniCoder they're trying to install is a dev tool with frontend/backend components that build with Docker, not a model file itself. The installation script at tesslate.com is asking how they want to serve the model backend. Given that they have llama-server running on port 8000 with no models loaded yet, the most straightforward option would be using the local llama.cpp server they already have running.\n\nSince we're currently downloading the OmniCoder GGUF file which will eventually live at ~/Models/gguf/, once that completes I can load it into llama-server. So the best choice is option 3 (local llama.cpp at localhost:8000), since we already have the server infrastructure in place.","thinkingSignature":"916879a9d52342ea439bfda536dda13261be2db3ffde7aa617d75a176b2098e7"},{"type":"text","text":"你已经装了 `llama-server` 在 **localhost:8000**，选 **3) Local llama.cpp (localhost:8000)**。\n\n不过下载的 OmniCoder GGUF 文件还没下完（之前卡在 327MB 了）。让我先把它下完：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ecwl1hmuy4q1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -lh /Users/ling/Models/gguf/omnicoder-9b-q5_k_m.gguf 2>/dev/null\npgrep -f \"curl.*omnicoder\" 2>/dev/null && echo \"下载中\" || echo \"未在下载\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77,"output":438,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":89809,"totalTokens":90324,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775729655991,"responseId":"0626aef8b44b1f3a7bb36d75b43f04c1"}}
