{"type":"message","id":"ac67a07e","parentId":"1e184444","timestamp":"2026-04-09T13:55:00.832Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that downloading via command line is too slow, and asking if it's a source issue. The hf-mirror.com has been very slow and unreliable. Let me check if there's a different mirror or approach that could be faster. \n\nActually, the issue might be that hf-mirror.com is rate-limiting or has poor bandwidth. Let me think about alternatives:\n\n1. The original HuggingFace might be faster if the user has HF_TOKEN set up\n2. There might be other Chinese mirrors like modelscope.cn\n3. The user could download directly from their browser which might be faster\n4. There's also the option to download a smaller quantization\n\n\n5. I should give them some practical alternatives\n\nThe core problem is the mirror's bandwidth constraints. I could suggest trying a different download method like a browser with an HF token, switching to ModelScope as an alternative source, or using a smaller model variant to speed things up. Since they're running the Tesslate Studio install script anyway, they might be able to download the file through the browser instead, which could be faster than command-line fetching from the mirror.","thinkingSignature":"e52fa5842c2282119c96dddcf68384b6ea311cf54dd9d059cea9a53024b6ab5e"},{"type":"text","text":"是的，hf-mirror.com 带宽不稳定，速度很慢。有几个方案：\n\n**方案 1：换镜像站**\n```bash\n# 试 HuggingFace 官方（需要 HF_TOKEN）\nHF_TOKEN=你的token wget -c \"https://huggingface.co/Tesslate/OmniCoder-9B-GGUF/resolve/main/omnicoder-9b-q5_k_m.gguf\" -O ~/Models/gguf/omnicoder-9b-q5_k_m.gguf\n```\n\n**方案 2：用浏览器下载（最快）**\n直接用浏览器打开：\n```\nhttps://hf-mirror.com/Tesslate/OmniCoder-9B-GGUF/tree/main\n```\n然后下载 `omnicoder-9b-q5_k_m.gguf`，浏览器下载速度通常比命令行快很多。\n\n**方案 3：换小一点的量化版本**\nQ4_K_M 只有 3.6GB（vs Q5_K_M 的 6.5GB），质量差距很小：\n```bash\nwget -c \"https://hf-mirror.com/Tesslate/OmniCoder-9B-GGUF/resolve/main/omnicoder-9b-q4_k_m.gguf\" -O ~/Models/gguf/omnicoder-9b-q4_k_m.gguf\n```\n\n**方案 4：用国内 ModelScope（最快）**\nModelScope 是阿里云的，国内速度极快：\n```bash\npip install modelscope && \\\nmodelscope download --model_id Tesslate/OmniCoder-9B-GGUF --filename omnicoder-9b-q4_k_m.gguf --local_dir ~/Models/gguf\n```\n\n你想用哪个方案？浏览器下载最简单，或者我可以帮你试 ModelScope。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77,"output":599,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":97489,"totalTokens":98165,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775742879289,"responseId":"0626e29f72b08b25ecd08e32f454dfa8"}}
