{"type":"message","id":"440c872f","parentId":"66835c26","timestamp":"2026-04-09T14:02:31.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file is 0 bytes. ModelScope is connecting but not downloading anything. This is likely a network issue with ModelScope too. Let me try the direct browser download approach, which is the most reliable.\n\nActually, let me think about what other options there are:\n\n1. The user can download directly in the browser from `https://modelscope.cn/models/Tesslate/OmniCoder-9B-GGUF/files` \n2. Or from HuggingFace mirror directly in browser\n3. The wget download was slow but progressing\n\nActually, looking at the situation:\n- wget was downloading at ~100MB/min but kept getting interrupted/stopped\n\n\n- Both HuggingFace mirror and ModelScope are failing entirely\n- The real issue is just network connectivity to HuggingFace\n\nI should give the user the most practical advice: use their browser to download directly, or if they have good cloud server access, download from there and transfer the file over. Let me just share the direct download links they can use in their browser.","thinkingSignature":"e0e59919c1ed1146888a3004c5ac1e911d6e11a66d97e527a763869587447425"},{"type":"text","text":"ModelScope 也是 0 bytes，网络有问题。最可靠的方法：\n\n**直接用浏览器下载：**\n\n1. 打开：`https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Tesslate/OmniCoder-9B-GGUF/files`\n\n2. 点击 `omnicoder-9b-q4_k_m.gguf` 下载（3.6GB）\n\n3. 下载完放到 `~/Models/gguf/`，告诉我\n\n---\n\n**或者如果你有手机热点**，可以试试用手机网络开热点给电脑，下载会快很多。\n\n**最快的方案**：如果你有阿里云服务器，在服务器上用 ModelScope 下载（内网速度极快），再传到 Mac：\n\n```bash\n# 在服务器上执行\npip install modelscope\nmodelscope download \"Tesslate/OmniCoder-9B-GGUF\" omnicoder-9b-q4_k_m.gguf --local_dir /your/path\n```\n\n你试哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":82760,"output":407,"cacheRead":20165,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103332,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason"