{"type":"message","id":"2cd3ebff","parentId":"a6a0f30d","timestamp":"2026-04-09T14:10:01.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that the sector-sync agent has 09:00 and 09:20 schedules, but no post-market (after 15:00) schedule. I need to add a 15:30 or 16:00 post-market sync. Also, I should add a dashboard generation job that runs after the sector sync.Let me update the sector-sync plist to add a 15:30 post-market sync, and also add a dashboard generation job.Actually, let me think about this more carefully. The sector sync runs at 09:00 and 09:20. But during the trading day, the data should be fresh. The issue is that after market closes at 15:00, there's no refresh. \n\nI'll add a 15:30 post-market sync for all weekdays and create a separate launchd agent to generate the dashboard after the sector data is refreshed.","thinkingSignature":"3c5121220f11f7d60402a90225a0d1530adc33ac1b1667f020fc7ddad3e2412c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g3smojf3hil3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > ~/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.openclaw.quant.sector-sync.plist << 'EOF'\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC \"-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN\" \"http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd\">\n<plist version=\"1.0\">\n<dict>\n    <key>Label</key>\n    <string>ai.openclaw.quant.sector-sync</string>\n    <key>User</key>\n    <string>ling</string>\n    <key>ProgramArguments</key>\n    <array>\n        <string>/usr/bin/python3</string>\n        <string>/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/sync_sector_board_data.py</string>\n    </array>\n    <key>WorkingDirectory</key>\n    <string>/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system</string>\n    <key>StandardOutPath</key>\n    <string>/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/sector_sync.log</string>\n    <key>StandardErrorPath</key>\n    <string>/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspa