{"type":"message","id":"6270e561","parentId":"d981ff05","timestamp":"2026-04-09T14:10:23.390Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why I'm still showing as MiniMax when they asked to switch to GLM-5.1. This is likely because this is still the same session that was started with MiniMax. The config change I made would only take effect for new sessions. I should explain this.","thinkingSignature":"e733dbc4f8bc5599c904f7aba1a8414dfe22d0bd1bd6f485997ee536572e16c7"},{"type":"text","text":"当前这个会话是在配置切换**之前**启动的，所以还是用 MiniMax。\n\n新消息会开**新 session**，那时候才会用 GLM-5.1。\n\n你在飞书里**重新发一条消息**给我，就是 GLM-5.1 了。当前这条回复还是 MiniMax 的 session。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":126,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":112518,"totalTokens":112736,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775743807688,"responseId":"0626e63f5573df8d238475ba4aa43a79"}}
